properties.description: Drops about 25 feet down a narrow slot to a pool below. Can be downclimbed but the dirt is clay like and could be slippery. The pool could be up to chest deep.

properties.name: R2
properties.description: Drops about 15 feet to a pool at the bottom that can bee waist to chest deep.

properties.name: R3
properties.description: Drops about 20 feet and is downclimbable with moderate skills.
